I'm an ganguro girl enthusiast and I make my own works.
I use AI assistance but all my art goes through a rigorous editing/fixing process until I find it acceptable.

Quality > Quantity

I don't like simple art [people just standing, posing, etc] that are being made with AI, so I strive to make AI content that are high quality or technically challenging.
All the art I post goes through time-consuming editing to make sure hands, eyes, and composition are nearly perfect.
